,"height":198}},{"text":"Pain Point 3: 아티스트 공백기의 콘텐츠 부족","targetRectangle":{"y":621.93219709396362,"x":2018.957763671875,"width":496.50351562500009,"height":41.279999971389771}},{"text":"[cite_start]아티스트 활동이 없으면 플랫폼 트래픽과 팬 활동이 급감.","targetRectangle":{"y":663.21219706535339,"x":2047.2077639102936,"width":737.20839843749991,"height":41.279999971389771}},{"text":"붙여넣은 동영상.png","targetRectangle":{"y":1410.5062255859375,"x":1640.692626953125,"width":1246.3065185546875,"height":402.306640625}},{"text":"X","targetRectangle":{"y":1218.146484375,"x":156.1339111328125,"width":56.1962890625,"height":102}},{"text":"붙여넣은 동영상.png","targetRectangle":{"y":156.19805908203125,"x":114.05363464355469,"width":1730,"height":1006.7392578125}},{"text":"파편화, 평면적 정보 ","targetRectangle":{"y":1129.550048828125,"x":762.20480364787591,"width":576.53120056176181,"height":104}},{"text":"어려운 정보 습득","targetRectangle":{"y":1301.9473876953125,"x":585.21651930432313,"width":412.24320035018923,"height":89}},{"text":"아티스트를 알아가고 싶을 때 어떻게 알아가야하는지 모름. 어렵다. ","targetRectangle":{"y":1114.5394287109375,"x":1269.7067584991455,"width":765.23279999999977,"height":36.727616434097399}},{"text":"새로운 아티스트를 입덕하고 ","targetRectangle":{"y":1148.4141190517516,"x":1269.7067584991455,"width":328.34591999999998,"height":64.177617077827563}},{"text":"어디서 무엇부터 파악해야하는지 봐야하는 것들이 정해져있지 않아서 진입장벽이 높다.","targetRectangle":{"y":1268.7707935076858,"x":1269.7067584991455,"width":985.03775999999925,"height":64.177617077827335}},{"text":"이 때 아티스트 마인드맵을 보면서 공부가능","targetRectangle":{"y":1330.0954844922301,"x":1269.7067584991455,"width":496.58879999999999,"height":64.177617077827335}},{"text":"팬이어도 최신 이슈 파악, 주요활동 정리에 유용","targetRectangle":{"y":1391.4201754767744,"x":1269.7067584991455,"width":538.19567999999981,"height":64.177617077827563}},{"text":"입덕 1일차, 뭐부터 봐야 할지 막막하다면? ","targetRectangle":{"y":1511.7768499327085,"x":1269.7067584991455,"width":494.77343999999994,"height":64.177617077827563}},{"text":"Knowledge Graph > NotebookLM","target